Kamed Studio Warszawa

Na kolejne dni zdjeciowe do nowo powstającej historii pewnego zespołu poszukuje statystów kobiet i mężczyzn.

📍Na jutro 25.09 poszukujemy Państwa jako uczestników pielgrzymki.

Wiek 20-80 lat.

Osoby briefem wpisujące się w lata '80

Stawka 120 zł netto

Zgłoszenia prosimy wysyłać na adres mailowy :

Janekbo2025@gmail.com załączając :

📌 2 aktualne dobrej jakosci, aktualne zdjecia twarzy i sylwetki

📌 Wiek

📌 Imię i nazwisko

📌 Nr telefonu

📌 Wymiary.

Z dopiskiem  25.09

items.text:
‼️ WARSZAWA KONTYNUACJE ‼️

Do nowych projektów, których akcja dzieje się w latach współczesnych, poszukujemy:

▪️ OPCJA 1- kobiet i mężczyzn w wieku 20-50 lat jako pracowników schroniska. Plan w dniach 29-30.09 i 1.10. Stawka za 3 dni, w zależności od godzin, 420-480 zł. 

▪️ OPCJA 2- kobiet i mężczyzn w wieku ok 30-40 lat. Plan w dniach 2-3.10. Stawka za dwa dni, w zależności od godzin, 280-320 zł.

Jest to OBOWIĄZKOWA KONTYNUACJA! W mailu proszę o załączenie informacji o wybranej opcji. 

Zgłoszenia wraz z imieniem i nazwiskiem, numerem telefonu, AKTUALNYMI zdjęciami (sylwetka, twarz), przyjmujemy na adres: KAROLINA@ONSETAGENCY.PL w tytule wpisując „NOWE”.

sharedPost.text:
**WARSZAWA / ŻYRARDÓW / SOCHACZEW**

**30 września i 11 października**

Szukam Statystów na plan filmu krótkometrażowego na 2 dni kontynuacyjne.

- Plan 30 września jest w Puszczy Mariańskiej niedaleko Żyrardowa.
-Plan 11 października w Sochaczewie.

Gramy lata 70te, nie ma wymagań co do wyglądu i wieku.

Dojazd we własnym zakresie dlatego szukam osób z autem, które zgodzą się zabrać 2/3 lub nawet 4 osoby.

Jest zwrot kosztów paliwa.

Plan kameralny, zapewnione pełne wyżywienie, jest gdzie spocząć 

**Stawka 130 zł za dzień zdjęciowy. Łącznie 260 zł za 2 dni**

W zgłoszeniu poproszę informację odnośnie auta. Pasażer czy Kierowca? 

ZGŁOSZENIA:

Poproszę na adres: **ewelina.wika@podtytulem.pl**

W tytule maila: **FILM K2**

W treści: imię i nazwisko, wiek, nr telefonu, miejscowość

W załączniku:

– aktualne, dobrej jakości zdjęcie twarzy (portret, w dziennym świetle, bez filtrów)

attachments.ocrText: May be an image of 3 people and text that says 'SZUKAMY STATYSTÓW! WARSZAWA WARSZAWA/ŻYRARDÓW/SOCHACZEW ŻYRARDÓW /SOCHACZEW 30 września i 11 pażdziernika (Kontynuacja) Stawka 130zł Zgłoszenia Zgłoszenia na adres ewelina.wika@podtytulem.pl ewelina.w PODI TYTUŁEM'

sharedPost.text:
🌟🌟🌟!!! PILNY CASTING !!!🌟🌟🌟

Poszukujemy naturalnej  modelki/ aktorki w wieku 20-30 lat. 

Typ urody Caucasian / słowiański. Kolor włosów dowolny.

Wiek: 20-28 lat

Stawki od 3000-5800zł 

UWAGA: Zgłoszenia DZIŚ do godziny 18:00

Szczegóły podaję zainteresowanym na priv.

**HALO KRAKÓW I OKOLICE **

Do filmu "LALKA" tym razem szukamy Statystów

Panowie 18 - 70 lat

**4.10.25 SOBOTA i 5.10.25 NIEDZIELA  TYNIEC -Role kontynuacyjne**

**6.10.25 PONIEDZIAŁEK - KRAKÓW  **

**Bardzo ważne - Wytyczne charakteryzacji**:

**wspólne:**

– bez widocznych tatuaży

– bez kolczyków w nosie, brwi, wargach

– naturalne kolory włosów

**Panowie:**

– męskie fryzury nie mogą być strzyżone maszynkami , tylko nożyczkami

– nie było włosów podgolonych, były one raczej dłuższe w różny sposób zaczesywane

– mogą być u Panów baki i wąsy.

– brody (nie mogą to być współczesne barberowe brody)

– naturalne kolory włosów bez farb i odsiwiaczy

**ZGŁOSZENIA**

Zgłoszenia poproszę na adres: **jarek.drzycimski@podtytulem.pl**

*W tytule:* **L4,5 lub L 6 - **w zależności od wyboru dnia  

*W treści:* imię i nazwisko, wiek, nr telefonu, miejscowość + wymiary: wzrost, klatka, pas, biodra, rozmiar ubrania i buta + kołnierzyk i obwód głowy  - dodatkowo zdjęcie z profilu

*W załączniku:* **ZDJĘCIE TWARZY I SYLWETKI**: **tylko z dnia zgłoszenia.**

Portretowe selfie w dziennym świetle, na wprost, patrząc w obiektyw. Bez żadnych filtrów. Bez okularów. Bez nakrycia głowy.

Hello everyone,

While I’m still quite new in this industry of both modelling and acting, I’d just like to put myself out there more

items.text:
KIELCE 
Hejka! 🎬�Jestem młodą osobą, która od dziecka interesuje się reżyserią i zawsze marzyła o tworzeniu filmów. Teraz chciałabym zebrać ekipę ludzi o podobnych zajawkach i wspólnie zacząć tworzyć amatorskie produkcje fabularne.
Szukam uczniów szkół średnich i studentów, którzy chcieliby spróbować swoich sił w filmie – niezależnie od doświadczenia. Może kręci Cię aktorstwo, scenariusz, kamera, montaż albo organizacja na planie? Każdy znajdzie tu miejsce.
Na razie startujemy totalnie od zera i w pełni amatorsko, ale z pasją i otwartością na pomysły 😉�Jeśli brzmi to jak coś dla Ciebie – odezwij się! Może razem uda nam się stworzyć coś naprawdę fajnego 🚀

items.text:
✨ BIG CREATIVE ANNOUNCEMENT! ✨ 

I’m beyond excited to officially introduce One World Studios HQ — a brand NEW multi-room creative content space in Baltimore, MD built for visionaries, storytellers, and creators of every kind.

Here’s what awaits you:

• 🎥 All-White Photography & Video Room – the perfect blank canvas.
• 🎙️ Podcast & Live Stream Studio – ready to record and broadcast.
• 🎬 Fully Equipped Live Talk Show Set – with a backstage walk-on experience.
• 📺 4K Multi-Camera + Switcher – professional-grade production tools.
• 🎞️ Film/Movie Series Design Space – bring your cinematic vision to life.
• 🏢 47,000 SQ FT of Open Space – or simply a clean, inspiring environment to create your vision.

One World Studios HQ was designed for creators who want an affordable, exclusive, and welcoming environment to produce their next big project.

Additional amenities include:

🍻 On-site brewery with food options
🅿️ 24-hour parking
💡 Stocked furniture, lighting, wireless & wired mic systems
☕ Cozy hospitality nook
…and much more.

📩 Inquire Today: info@OneWorldStudiosHQ.com

💡 We’ll even help you create a custom budget or payment plan that fits your production needs.

Your vision deserves a space where it can truly shine—let’s build it together at One World Studios HQ.

Feel free to REPOST and SHARE to someone who perhaps need help bringing their vision/brand/product to Life.

✨ BIG CREATIVE ANNOUNCEMENT! ✨ 

I’m beyond excited to officially introduce One World Studios HQ — a brand NEW multi-room creative content space in Baltimore, MD built for visionaries, storytellers, and creators of every kind.

Here’s what awaits you:

• 🎥 All-White Photography & Video Room – the perfect blank canvas.
• 🎙️ Podcast & Live Stream Studio – ready to record and broadcast.
• 🎬 Fully Equipped Live Talk Show Set – with a backstage walk-on experience.
• 📺 4K Multi-Camera + Switcher – professional-grade production tools.
• 🎞️ Film/Movie Series Design Space – bring your cinematic vision to life.
• 🏢 47,000 SQ FT of Open Space – or simply a clean, inspiring environment to create your vision.

One World Studios HQ was designed for creators who want an affordable, exclusive, and welcoming environment to produce their next big project.

Additional amenities include:

🍻 On-site brewery with food options
🅿️ 24-hour parking
💡 Stocked furniture, lighting, wireless & wired mic systems
☕ Cozy hospitality nook
…and much more.

📩 Inquire Today: info@OneWorldStudiosHQ.com

💡 We’ll even help you create a custom budget or payment plan that fits your production needs.

Your vision deserves a space where it can truly shine—let’s build it together at One World Studios HQ.

Feel free to REPOST and SHARE to someone who perhaps need help bringing their vision/brand/product to Life.

***PAID OPPORTUNITY* – OMG STORIES**

📢 Calling all storytellers, survivors, and secret-keepers…

Do you have a jaw-dropping story that no one believes actually happened?

Something wild, shocking, or totally unforgettable?

We’re filming a brand-new series for the hit YouTube channel OMG Stories **(450k)** , where real people share the most unbelievable things they’ve ever been through - from insane twists of fate to dark secrets, betrayals, and life-changing moments.

🎥 This is a PAID opportunity and filming happens in a London studio.

If that sounds like you (or someone you know), get in touch!

📧 Send your story to **[mireille.lee@upstream-media.co.uk](mailto:mireille.lee@upstream-media.co.uk)**

https://www.youtube.com/@OMG_stories

‼️NORTHWEST BIPOC ENTERTAINERS‼️

We are actively seeking talented BIPOC performers to bring beloved characters such as; Princess Tiana, Mulan, Mirabel, Jasmine, Moana, iconic Korean figures and more to life through engaging and authentic performances.

To our company representation matters! We are committed to celebrating the rich cultural heritage of these characters embodied by casting performers who reflect their backgrounds. Whether you're an experienced entertainer or a passionate newcomer, if you have a love for storytelling, performance, and creating magical moments for audiences of all ages, we invite you to join us in inspiring the next generation through inclusive and empowering portrayals.

Please PM Ever Enchanted Events or email everenchantedevent@gmail.com with a headshot, CV and a little about yourself and your background🥰⭐️

items.text:
📢Volunteers Wanted - Videographers! Liverpool Mystery Event📢

CAJ Productions is looking for 2 more reliable volunteers to help with a one-off mystery stunt in Liverpool City Centre on Saturday 20th September 2025.

It's part of a brand-new UK theatre tour coming in 2026, and this will be one of our headline public marketing stunts. 

The role is simple, but really important:

. Filming the event (reactions) on a phone (2 people required)

What you'll get:

. Travel expenses covered

. Be part of an unusual, exciting event that's going to get a lot of attention

. Something different to talk about (and looks great on a CV for anyone in events, film, or theatre)

If you're free, reliable, and up for being part of something mysterious and fun, drop me a message here or comment below and I'll share the details.

Thanks! 

Charlie

# **EILIG! **
**CASTING-AUFRUF – UGC-Videodreh für Immobilienprojekt in Heidelberg // 25.09.2025**

 **Drehort:** Heidelberg

 **Drehtag:** Freitag, 25. September 2025 – Start: 10:00 Uhr

 **Dauer:** ca. 4–5 Stunden (halber Drehtag)

 **Honorar:** 500 € Pauschalgage
** Was wir drehen:**

Für unseren Kunden – ein Immobilienunternehmen aus Leipzig – produzieren wir **15-20 kurze UGC-Videos** (User Generated Content), die für **Social Media & Online-Ads** eingesetzt werden.

Die Clips bestehen aus **authentischen Monologen**, die direkt in die Kamera gesprochen werden: **klar, sympathisch, ruhig und professionell**.
* Skriptlänge: 40–60 Sekunden pro Clip
* Teleprompter ist vor Ort (kein Auswendiglernen nötig)
* Fokus: **seriöse, glaubwürdige Darstellung**
** Wen wir suchen:**

 **1 Schauspielerin *****(weiblich)***
* Alter: 25–35 Jahre
* Look: gepflegt, urban, authentisch-professionell (z. B. „Young Professional“-Vibe – denkbar wären Start-up-Gründer, Immobilienberater, Creator mit Vertrauensausstrahlung)
* Sprache: Hochdeutsch, **klare Artikulation** und sichere Präsenz vor der Kamera
* Erfahrung mit Social Media Ads ist ein Plus, aber **keine Voraussetzung**
** Über uns:**

Wir sind die **IMMO 4.0 GmbH**, ein Performance-Marketing-Unternehmen aus Heidelberg.

Unser Schwerpunkt: **Marketingkampagnen für Immobilienvertriebe, Bauträger und Kapitalanlagen im gesamten DACH-Raum**.

Wir setzen auf **echtes Storytelling und professionell produzierten UGC-Content**, um seriöse Projekte authentisch darzustellen.
** Das bieten wir Dir:**
* 500 € Pauschalgage
* Teleprompter & eingespielte Crew vor Ort
* Styling-Hinweise & Text-Input durch uns (kein Kostüm notwendig, clean/professionell reicht)
* Reelfähige Referenz für Deine Mappe
* Zusammenarbeit mit erfahrenem Videoteam in lockerer, produktiver Atmosphäre
** Bewerbung:**

Bitte sende uns so schnell wie möglich Deine Bewerbung mit:
* 2–3 aktuellen Bildern oder Showreel
* Kurzprofil (Name, Alter, Standort)
* Optional: Link zu Instagram / Agenturseite / eigenen Reels

 Betreff: **„UGC-Videodreh Heidelberg – Vorname Nachname“**

 Bewerbung per WhatsApp an: **+49 172 7042469 (Phillip Kirillov – IMMO 4.0 GmbH)**

Unser Schwerpunkt: **Marketingkampagnen für Immobilienvertriebe, Bauträger und Kapitalanlagen im gesamten DACH-Raum**.

Wir setzen auf **echtes Storytelling und professionell produzierten UGC-Content**, um seriöse Projekte authentisch darzustellen.

**🔹 Das bieten wir Dir:**

* 500 € Pauschalgage
* Teleprompter & eingespielte Crew vor Ort
* Styling-Hinweise & Text-Input durch uns (kein Kostüm notwendig, clean/professionell reicht)
* Reelfähige Referenz für Deine Mappe
* Zusammenarbeit mit erfahrenem Videoteam in lockerer, produktiver Atmosphäre

**🔹 Bewerbung:**

Bitte sende uns so schnell wie möglich Deine Bewerbung mit:

* 2–3 aktuellen Bildern oder Showreel
* Kurzprofil (Name, Alter, Standort)
* Optional: Link zu Instagram / Agenturseite / eigenen Reels

👉 Betreff: **„UGC-Videodreh Leipzig – Vorname Nachname“**

👉 Bewerbung per WhatsApp an: **+49 172 7042469 (Phillip Kirillov – IMMO 4.0 GmbH)**

items.text:
Female Host – Horror/True Crime Talk Show
Location: Burbank, California (or surrounding areas)

We are seeking a dynamic female host to join our on-camera team for a horror and true crime–focused web series. This role requires someone with strong on-screen presence, a passion for horror, true crime, and the supernatural, and the ability to engage with both co-hosts and guests in a lively, authentic way.

Responsibilities:
 • Co-host alongside two main hosts during live-taped shows.
 • Contribute knowledge and insights on horror, true crime, and supernatural subjects.
 • Engage with guests, audience members, and co-hosts with energy and professionalism.
 • Help shape conversations that are informative, entertaining, and on-brand.

Requirements:
 • Female host talent based in Burbank, California, or nearby areas.
 • Strong knowledge of horror, true crime, and supernatural genres.
 • Confident on-camera presence and strong improvisational/conversational skills.
 • Ability to work collaboratively with other hosts.
 • Must be available for scheduled back-to-back tapings.
 • We are especially interested in candidates who already have a horror-style look or aesthetic that fits the tone of the show.

Compensation & Perks:
 • $500 per show.
 • We film two shows back-to-back per shoot day.
 • If selected, we will privately share details of the show and company.
 • All employees receive a quarterly bonus based on the show’s performance.
 • Small, tight-knit crew where every team member receives a percentage of the show’s profits.
 • Immediate hire.

How to Apply:

Please submit the following materials:
 • Headshot (highlighting your look and style).
 • Demo reel or on-camera sample (hosting, acting, or relevant video work).
 • Resume with relevant experience.
 • A brief note on why you’re passionate about horror/true crime/supernatural.

Submit to VCSales505@gmail.com

topComments.text: Interested. I will email. I have a strong knowledge of the occult and supernatural

items.text:
**📣 Stellenausschreibung – TanzHaus Erfurt**

**Tanzpädagog:innen & Tanzlehrer:innen (m/w/d) gesucht**

**für verschiedene Tanzrichtungen – Festanstellung oder auf Honorarbasis**

**🕺 Über uns**

Das **TanzHaus Erfurt** ist eines der größten Tanzstudios in Thüringen mit rund 1000 Mitgliedern. Unser Programm umfasst ein breites Spektrum von **Hip Hop, Commercial, Urban Contemporary** über **Jazz, Modern Dance, Ballett** bis hin zu **Kindertanz, Fitness- und Paartanzkursen**. Mehrere Companies und Crews sind Teil unserer Schule.
Neben dem regulären Unterricht sind wir Gastgeber der **Internationalen Erfurter Sommertanztage** und kooperieren mit Dozent:innen aus aller Welt.

Zur Verstärkung unseres Teams suchen wir engagierte **Tanzlehrer:innen und Tanzpädagog:innen** für verschiedene Stilrichtungen.

**🎯 Dein Profil**
* Du unterrichtest einen oder mehrere Tanzstile (z. B. **Hip Hop, Commercial, Jazz, Contemporary, Ballett, Kindertanz**).
* Du hast Freude an der Arbeit mit verschiedenen Altersgruppen (Kinder, Jugendliche, Erwachsene) verschiedener Level (Anfänger bis Fortgeschrittene).
* Du verfügst über Unterrichtserfahrung oder eine pädagogische Ausbildung im Tanz.
* Du hast vielleicht Erfahrung bei der Entwicklung von Wettkampf-Choreografien.
* Du bist zuverlässig, teamorientiert und motiviert, **regelmäßig in Erfurt** zu unterrichten.

**💡 Wir bieten dir**
* **Mehrere feste Kurse pro Woche** – mit Option auf Ausbau.
* Möglichkeit einer **Festanstellung** (Vollzeit, Teilzeit, Midi- oder Minijob) oder attraktiver Honorartätigkeit.
* Eine moderne künstlerische Tanzschule mit professionell ausgestatteten Studios.
* Ein tolles Team, was dich mit offenen Armen empfängt.
* Eine lebendige Tanz-Community und Auftrittsmöglichkeiten bei Events & Projekten.
* Raum für deine Kreativität und Unterstützung bei der Umsetzung eigener Ideen.

**📍 Standort**

**TanzHaus Erfurt – im Herzen Thüringens, in der Mitte von Deutschland**
Zentrale Lage mit guter Erreichbarkeit (Leipzig, Halle, Jena, Weimar, Berlin, Frankfurt, Kassel, Hannover, Göttingen, Coburg, Bamberg, Nürnberg).

**📩 Bewerbung**

👉 Sende uns deine **kurze Vorstellung + Tanzvideo oder CV** an:
📧 info@tanzhaus-erfurt.de
☎️ 0176 41113147

**📢 DANCE&ARTS IS EXPANDING TO BIRMINGHAM! 🎭💃**

 

Exciting news! You’ve known us in London, and now… we’re bringing the magic to Birmingham too!

 

Dance&Arts is growing, and we're looking for **passionate dance, drama, and arts instructors to join our team in Birmingham**! If you love inspiring young talents, we want to hear from you!

 

✨ We’re hiring for:

✅ Dance (all styles)

✅ Drama

✅ Musical Theatre

✅ Basic Gymnastics (mat-based only)

✅ Arts & Crafts

 

💰 Pay: £30 per hour

 

📩 How to Apply: Send your **Enhanced DBS & CV to ****teachers@dancearts-uk.com** with your preferred position in the subject line.

 

Join us in bringing creativity, movement, and inspiration to the next generation! 🌟

 

#WeAreExpanding #HiringTeachers #DanceAndArts #TeachingOpportunities #BirminghamJobs #PerformingArts #CreativeEducation

items.text:
The first 10 mins of my first full length play Blackout 1985 is going to be performed as part of Wooden Arrow Productions next scratch evening on 30th October at Lamda at their Sainsburys Theatre!

The casting is UNPAID but there will be professional photography, industry guests for feedback and a chance to network after with the guests and the audience. There are also other roles in other plays that need filling. 

Deadline is this Saturday!

Synopsis of Blackout 1985: 28th September 1985. A day marked in history. The Lewis family gathers in their living room as the streets outside erupt in flames. Winston and Angie strive to protect their children, Jimmy and Asha, from a world that denies their humanity. As generational wounds, dreams, and tensions collide, the family must decide whether to stay safe behind closed doors or step into the fire of history. Blackout 1985 is the first in the trilogy, which shines a light on key Black British moments.

If you are interested or know anyone please go to this link - 
https://forms.gle/uJFMiQzyR6kVqBae8

🍁 **Sziasztok!** 🎬
Szerepelni vágyó fiatalokat keresek TV-s projektekhez, film- és reklámforgatásokra! 🍂📺✨

🍂 **Nyitott lehetőségek:**

🎥 **Háttér statiszta** filmekben, sorozatokban, reklámokban
💰 *Nettó napi bér: 8.000–20.000 Ft*

👏 **Közönség statiszta** a legnépszerűbb hazai és nemzetközi showműsorok forgatásán
💰 *Nettó napi bér: 5.000–8.000 Ft*

🌟 **Kiemelt statiszta** filmekben, sorozatokban, reklámokban vagy videoklipekben
💰 *Nettó napi bér: 20.000–40.000 Ft*

🎭 **Kisebb szereplő** filmekben, sorozatokban
💰 *Nettó napi bér: 40.000–60.000 Ft*

📍 **A forgatások helyszíne:** Budapest és vonzáskörzete
👫 Jelentkezni lehet párban is – hozd a barátodat/barátnődet!
📆 A munkavállalás rugalmas, nincs kötelező óraszám vagy minimum projekt
🍁 Új lehetőségek hetente!

📩 **Jelentkezni üzenetben tudtok nálam!**

🎥 **Háttér statiszta** filmekben, sorozatokban, reklámokban

👏 **Közönség statiszta** a legnépszerűbb hazai és nemzetközi showműsorok forgatásán
💰 *Nettó napi bér: 5.000–8.000 Ft*

🌟 **Kiemelt statiszta** filmekben, sorozatokban, reklámokban vagy videoklipekben
💰 *Nettó napi bér: 20.000–40.000 Ft*

🎭 **Kisebb szereplő** filmekben, sorozatokban

📍 **A forgatások helyszíne:** Budapest és vonzáskörzete

items.text:
Hi everyone, I'm Deividas 30, Lithuanian.

Model | Performer | Wellness Professional
With over 50 professional photoshoots under my belt — including paid projects across fashion, lifestyle, artistic, body paint, and life modeling — I have developed a versatile presence in front of the camera backed by a disciplined lifestyle and unique skillset.

Link below intro video
https://drive.google.com/file/d/19OcejTSRFWF2ZmQxdeoF92CEF7TKKAdb/view?usp=drivesdk

Alongside modeling, I bring on-screen experience from multiple TV shows, interview formats, podcasts, and extra appearances in my home country, while continuously expanding into acting and performance-based work.

Performance Skills
• Aerial Acrobatics — Hoop, Trapeze, Silks, Rope (Beginner–Intermediate)
• Contact Fire Staff — Intermediate
• Katana Wielding — Intermediate 
• Yoga — Advanced
• Swimming — Advanced
• Parkour - Intermediate
• Dancing - non professional but confident dancer

I’m currently seeking freelance work as model/actor/performer and agency representation (available internationally). Open to test shoots, collaborations, and paid opportunities.

✨ Updated measurements (as of Sept 22, 2025):
Height: 195cm
Chest: 41
Waist: 32
Hips: 37.5
Neck: 16
Sleeve: 32 (81.5cm)
Inseam: 32 (81.5cm)
Outseam: 36.4 (92.3cm)
Shoulder Width: 19 (48.5cm)
Shoe: UK 10.5 (can do 10–11) | EU 44–46

🌍 Based in London | Available worldwide

Professional Background
• Qualified Swimming Coach, Yoga Teacher, and Personal Trainer with 12+ years of teaching experience.
• Deep expertise in health, movement, breath, wellness, and high performance.

What Sets Me Apart
• Strong work ethic, relentless discipline, and ability to perform under discomfort, pressure, and challenging conditions.
• Holistic approach to self-regulation — always camera-ready, physically prepared, mentally sharp, and adaptable.
• Highly motivated in building my craft and presence — I create, edit, and post content daily across YouTube, TikTok, and Instagram to develop audience reach and on-camera charisma.

Current Focus
Seeking opportunities in modeling, acting, and performance — primarily in the UK (based in London ) but open to international projects. I’m committed to levelling up my skills, embracing bold creative challenges, and bringing exceptional authentic energy, professionalism, and reliability to every collaboration.

If you need anything else please let me know 

Kindest regards 
Deividas Juozapavičius
+12022558377
Instagram: @deivjuo
YouTube: @deivjuo
TikTok: @deivjuo

items.text:
**CASTING CALL – CAST**
Vi søger medvirkende til en kort optagelse d. **2. oktober** i **Københavnsområdet**.

**Optagelser:** Københavnsområdet 
**Varighed:** 3–4 timer
**Honorar:** (B-honorar) --> mere info på mail 
**Rettigheder:** Video, stills + 2 outdoor placeringer

**Alle køn **
**Alder:** 25-55 år

**CASTING BRIEF**

Scenen foregår ved en grønthandler foran to store kasser med identiske appelsiner:

Kim står smilende og kigger på de billige appelsiner – underspillet selvtilfreds.
Gert står nervøst og forvirret. Han rækker langsomt ud efter de dyre appelsiner og kigger nervøst på Kim, der følger hans bevægelse.
Kim tager en håndfuld billige appelsiner med stor selvfølgelighed.
Gert bliver fortabt og forvirret tilbage.

**SELFTAPE**

Indspil gerne to korte takes: ét som Kim og ét som Gert.
Hold det enkelt – ingen rekvisitter er nødvendige.

Send selftape til: **statist@isaacproduction.com**
Deadline: Snarest muligt – optagelser er d. 2. oktober

items.text:
(Skuespillerinde👩‍🦳) p.s. “i alderen fra 26 - 51.” søges til en rolle som Psykolog/coach hvor du skal spille overfor en mandlig skuespiller der har Skizofreni. 
Filmen hedder Aske til Liv.
Alle optagelser vil foregå i Odense By, omegn, så vigtigt at du kan tiltræde ved hurtig virkning og spontane optagelser. Der er fundet tilladelse til lån af lejlighed og alle andre skuespiller, statister er castet. Optagelser der mangler er mødet med hovedpersonen og et par dages optagelser i lejligheden og nogle udendørsscener. Venligst skriv tilbage i Messenger ved interesse... 🎥🙏😉

Stage combat training in the southwest this November!! ⚔️⚔️⚔️

LIMITED SPACES REMAINING!

Early bird price only available for 6 more days!

This course is suitable for beginners and open to anyone with an interest in dramatic combat. It will cover single sword and unarmed techniques that will culminate in a fight performance.

Upon completion you will receive a standard level industry recognised certification from the British Academy of Dramatic Combat! (It looks great on your CV!)

Early bird price: £275
Standard price: £300

Please feel free to DM me for more information. Link to book below!

https://www.eventbrite.co.uk/e/badc-standard-level-intensive-unarmed-single-sword-tickets-1564037441089?aff=oddtdtcreator

items.text:
🎃Halloween acting job opportunity🎃

🎃 Join the Cast of Halloween at Winstanley Park! 👻✨

We’re searching for fun, energetic, and family-friendly performers to bring the magic of Halloween to life at Winstanley Park’s half-term events this October!

Event Details:
 • 📅 Event Dates: 25th – 31st October
 • ⏰ Times: 10:00am – 4:30pm daily
 • 💷 Run Rate: £1050 for the full event

Rehearsals (attendance required):
 • 🗓️ Rehearsal: 17th October
 • 🗓️ Dress Run: 21st October

What We’re Looking For:
 • Friendly, engaging performers who love interacting with children and families
 • Ability to stay in character and create a magical, seasonal atmosphere
 • Great storytelling and improvisation skills
 • Previous experience in theatre, children’s entertainment, or immersive events is a plus
 • ✅ Must hold a valid DBS check

What You’ll Get:
 • A competitive run rate
 • The chance to create unforgettable Halloween memories for families

items.text:
**CASTING-AUFRUF – UGC-Videodreh für Immobilienprojekt in Heidelberg // Donnerstag 25.09.2025**
 
Drehort: Heidelberg // Bahnstadt

Drehtag: 25.09.2025 - 10.00 Uhr
 
Geplanter Drehzeitraum: halber Drehtag (4–5 Stunden)
Schauspielhonorar: 500 € pauschal
Was wir drehen:

Für unseren Kunden, einen Immobilienunternehmen aus Hamburg, produzieren wir 25 kurze UGC-Videos (User Generated Content) für Social Media & Online-Ads. Die Videos sind authentisch gesprochene Clips, die direkt in die Kamera eingesprochen werden – klar, sympathisch, ruhig.

Skriptlänge pro Video: 40–60 Sekunden, ein Teleprompter ist vor Ort – keine Auswendiglernerei notwendig.
 
Gesucht werden:
* 1 Schauspielerin & 1 Schauspieler
* Alter: 28–40 Jahre
* Look: authentisch, gepflegt, urban-professionell – ein natürlicher „Young Professional“-Vibe (Think: Start-up, Immobilienberater, Creator mit Vertrauensausstrahlung)
* Sprache: Hochdeutsch, sichere Sprechweise, gute Artikulation
* Erfahrung mit Kamera & Social Media Ads von Vorteil, aber keine Voraussetzung
Über uns:

Wir sind die IMMO 4.0 GmbH, ein Performance-Marketing-Unternehmen aus Heidelberg.

Wir entwickeln Marketingkampagnen für Immobilienvertriebe, Bauträger und Kapitalanlageprodukte im DACH-Raum – und setzen dabei bewusst auf echtes, greifbares Storytelling mit professionellem UGC-Content.

Das bieten wir Dir:
* 500 € Pauschalgage
* Teleprompter + eingespielte Crew vor Ort
* Styling & Text-Input durch uns (kein Kostüm notwendig, clean/professionell reicht)
* Reelfähige Referenz für Deine Mappe
* Zusammenarbeit mit erfahrenem Videoteam in lockerer, produktiver Atmosphäre

Bewerbung:

Bitte sende uns bis asap Deine Bewerbung mit:
* 2–3 aktuellen Bildern oder Showreel
* Kurzprofil (Name, Alter, Standort)
* Optional: Link zu Instagram / Agenturseite / Eigenen Reels
* Betreff: „UGC-Videodreh Heidelberg – Vorname Nachname“

Bewerbung bitte per WhatsApp an: +49 172 7042469

(Phillip Kirillov - IMMO4.0 GmbH)

Hinweis:

Die finalen Produktionen erscheinen im Rahmen einer Online-Marketingkampagne für den Bereich Kapitalanlage-Immobilien. Seriös, hochwertig, glaubwürdig.

Wir freuen uns auf Deine Bewerbung – let’s create!

Dein Team von IMMO 4.0 GmbH

🚨URGENT CASTING CALL🚨

Project Title: SIO: Origins
Production Company: Museboxx M&F
Location: Darbyshire???? TBA (UK-based production)
Deadline: Urgent

Role: Co-Starring Leads – Names TBA
We’re casting for two dynamic male actors to take on a co-starring leading roles in our upcoming production, SIO: Origins, part of the larger SIO universe. The roles are emotionally charged and physically demanding, featuring performance across acting, dance, singing, and occasional stunt choreography. For these roles, We do have places for the characters to appear on the final episode of SIO:Echoes of the SIX - which has been airing throughout this year online. And to be a part of other SIO series', including live performances and other Muaeboxx projects.

Character Traits & Requirements:

• Sexuality: Gay & Bisexual
• Age: 26-28
• Height: 5ft 7 to 6ft
• Performance Abilities: Singer, Dancer, Acting and Rap
• Comfortable of doing own Stunts
• Comfortable with doing Gymnastics
• No piercings/jewelry

• Must be available for Live Performances

Previous experience in emotionally intense roles is a bonus

Payment & Contract:
Budget is currently being finalised. Payment details will be discussed at a later stage and confirmed in actor contracts. This will be a credited role with potential for expanded involvement in future series.

To Apply:
Send an email to museboxxmfcasting@gmail.com to send the following: Submit headshot, showreel (if available).
Audition scripts and details will be provided upon application.

If you have any issues with contacting the email above, please don't hesitate to contact our other email below - wintersxperia@gmail.com

More details about the projects will be discussed throughout the Audition process.

**CASTING CALL: BUSINESS OWNERS **

I’m currently casting for an exciting** QuickBooks project **featuring **UK-based entrepreneurs and business owners.**

We’re especially keen to hear from those with businesses turning over** £1 million+ per year**, but we **also welcome passionate founders operating at any level** — if your business has a brilliant story, we want to hear it.

This is a **paid opportunity** to feature in **YouTube gameshow-style content** — a fun and engaging way to promote your business to a wide audience.

Know someone? **Tag them here.**

Want to apply? **Email me at:** casper@casperblackcasting.com

Let’s shine a light on the UK’s most inspiring businesses 🔥🎬

items.text:
RUSH CASTING for "A-Z Murder Mystery"

This Project is a LIVE Murder Mystery Experience where everyone had a motive and the audience has to find the killer. (Like "Glass Onion"). Male talent should be a great storyteller and enjoy improv. 

Production Date: Saturday, November 15th

LENNY: 
African American Male
Age: 30-40’s; possibly older.

A confident, cocky Black male, Lenny is the flashy, fast-talking owner of one of the hottest music labels in the game. Strong, commanding presence.

To Request Sides:

📧 Submit to: PolishedImagesCasting@gmail.com

Subject line: A2Z - Aud926 - LENNY– your full name
(Ex: A2Z – Aud926 – LENNY– Polished Images)

 ✍🏽  Body of email: 
Contact info: Name, Email, Phone#
Social Media Links:
October Availability:

 🖇️ Attach:
Current Photo (Headshot)
Headshot holding something w/ Today’s Date

Sides will be sent upon receipt. 

Next steps: A Self-tape of the sides in Vertical format. Please record in Vertical (Portrait) format. Standing 

Full Submission Details:
Your Submission is due by 7pm, Friday, September 26th.

This is a PAID position. 

Good Luck! 

#Audition #Auditions  #ATL #Atlanta

Angela Boehm Casting is now looking for talent for a Promotional Video Shoot for 'OHIO JOBS'.

This project will be filming in October in Cleveland, OH, Columbus, OH, AND CINCINNATI, OH. (We have 18 Roles over 3 Different Cities).

Please read carefully below for details:

DETAILS:
- Project: 'OHIO JOBS' Promotional Shoot
- Project Location: Cleveland, OH (TBD) / Columbus, OH (TBD) / Cincinnati, OH (TBD)
- Date(s): October 7th / October 8th / October 9th / October 10th
- CALLBACK Date: Tuesday, September 30th (via Zoom)
- Rate: $500/10hr +20% per Session.
- Fitting Rate: $50/hr + 20% 
(Cincinnati Talent will fit on OCTOBER 6th. Columbus & Cleveland Talent will fit ON-SET)
- Usage: 2-Year Usage Buyout $2500 + 20% (Broadcast, Digital, Social, Print, OOH, Industrial)

WHAT WE'RE LOOKING FOR:
WE HAVE 18 ROLES OVER THE 3 OHIO CITIES FOR ALL AGES AND ETHNICITIES!!

Link to Roles & Cities they film: https://bit.ly/OhioJobsROLESandCITIES

SUBMISSION / AUDITION INSTRUCTIONS:
- Please email all auditions to: angela@angelaboehmcasting.com

- Deadline for Auditions is 9:00am on FRIDAY, SEPTEMBER 26th.

- SUBJECT LINE: OHIO JOBS Audition / (Your Name)
- Please have a blank background (DO NOT film outside).
- Please slate at the end of the audition (Slate can be in a separate video).

Slate Requirements:
- Full Name
- Agent (Phone number if you do not have an Agent)
- Location (PLEASE SLATE IF YOU'RE WILLING TO WORK LOCAL IN MORE THAN ONE OF THE MENTIONED CITIES)
- Please include in your slate a close-up of BOTH of your hands, FRONT & BACK!
- PLEASE SLATE ANY CONFLICTS ON FILMING/FITTING/CALLBACK DATES
- Please send the audition via Dropbox Folder or via WeTransfer Link (PLEASE MAKE SURE WE HAVE PERMISSION TO OPEN YOUR FILE).

Click below for the Audition Sides:
Link to Sides: https://bit.ly/OhioJobsSIDES

Kind regards,
Angela Boehm Casting Team

PLEASE NOTE: This is just a submission. If you are booked, we will reach out to YOU.

items.text:
Hi Everyone!

I'm a student studying filmmaking at **Birmingham City University**, and for one of our assignments, we are creating a **short film** and are looking for actors.

The concept isn't decided yet, but we are deciding between two:
1. A past chess champion reminisces about his glory days and replays the match that he lost in which started his downfall.
2. A girl whose inner self is screaming at her to help, while she is sucked into her phone, a film themed on how addicted we are to our phones.

We have a Test Shoot Day on the 23rd of October, 9:00am-12:00pm, and the Shoot Day is on the 4th of November, 9:00am-4:00pm. Both are at Parkside Building, Birmingham City University.

As we are students, this will be unpaid, unfortunately. But this is a great opportunity for actors who are starting out and want to get something on their resumes. We will include you in the credits.

We will have more details before the shoot, so don't worry.

If you are interested, please send an email to this address: **maisie.condron@mail.bcu.ac.uk**

Please include this information:

- Name

- Age

- Sex

- Location

- A self-tape of any performance

We will also be having more films come up in the future, so if you don't fit any of the roles described, you can still send an application in!

Thank you!

✨ Extras wanted for a rave scene! ✨

We’re shooting a nightclub scene for our experimental short film Falling Forward, Slightly tomorrow in Nørrebro, and we’d love some extra energy on the dance floor.

- Nørrebro

- 19:00–22:30 (just a few hours)

- Unpaid, but short, fun, and a chance to be part of a unique artistic project.

Falling Forward, Slightly is an experimental film about a swimmer, a fighter, and a dancer whose stories collide. It’s a passion project where we explore movement, sound, and atmosphere instead of dialogue.

We’ve already been filming some beautiful scenes (see stills below), and now it’s time for the rave!

If you want to join us and be part of the vibe, send me an email to **luciasanmiguel94@gmail.com**

wir suchen einen **männlichen UGC-Creator**, der in unseren Videos als eine Art **Experten-/Arztfigur** auftritt. Ein Arztkittel oder ähnliches wäre ideal, um den Gesundheitsaspekt zu unterstreichen.

 Wichtig:
* Du brauchst **keine eigenes Haustier** – es geht nur um deine Rolle als Experte.
* Videos sind Talking Head und sehr leicht umsetzbar.
* Script & Briefing bekommst du komplett von uns.

 Produkte stellen wir dir kostenlos zur Verfügung
 Ziel: **eine langfristige Zusammenarbeit mit vielen Projekten und regelmäßigem Content**

Wenn du Interesse hast, melde dich gerne per PN 

Liebe Grüße

Thomas

**$500 Finders Fee: Have You Been Ghosted By Your Husband Or Wife? (Docu-Series Casting)**

An acclaimed television production company and a major cable network are actively searching for women and men whose spouse has suddenly and mysteriously vanished, without warning, without explanation, and with no way to contact them. If you are still *legally married* but don’t know *where *your spouse is, you don’t have a clear explanation or *“why”* they left, or *how* to reach them, *we want to hear your story for a bold and empowering new series.*

**$500 Referral Fee: **Do You Know Someone? Share their information with us or simply have them tell us you referred them! Finders fee is paid IF referral is selected for production. 

*Selected for series candidates are compensated for taking part as well as receive expert help in tracking down their missing spouse, rebuilding their lives and finding closure. *

**To apply, please email: ****[casting@bodegapictures.com](mailto:casting@bodegapictures.com)****, **or visit: https://abandonedspouseshortapp.castingcrane.com/

Rosenteatret inviterer til audition på det velkendte og elskede stykke “Svend, Knud, og Valdemar”, historien om de tre danske konger… Eller faktisk er det mere en humoristisk historie om en skuespillertrup der prøver at sætte stykket op, men ALT går galt for dem 😆

Så er du klar på at få folk i salen til at grine over dine fjollerier, men kan du også spille seriøst, så er der lige præcis DIG vi mangler! 

PRAKTISK INFORMATION
- Tidspunkt: d. 29/9 kl. 19
- Sted: Rosenteatret (Teatertorvet 1, 8000 Århus C).
- Tilmelding: Skriv til lisbetlautrup@hotmail.com.

Auditionen foregår som en gruppeaudition, hvor i skal forberede jer hjemmefra på at fremføre første vers af “Jeg ved en lærkerede”, og efterfølgende får i tildelt nogle tekster i skal fremføre.

Hvis du ik kender stykket, kan vi anbefale at se det på YouTube ✨

NOW CASTING — Could YOU Be the Perfect Match for a TV Reality Star?

We’re launching a nationwide search for intelligent, confident, marriage-minded women (ages 23–33) who are ready for REAL love — and maybe even marriage — with a high-profile **TV Reality Star**.

This is your chance to meet one of reality TV’s most talked-about bachelors and see if sparks fly.

We’re looking for women who are:
✅ Intelligent, confident, and passionate about life
✅ Open-hearted, adventurous, and seeking a genuine relationship
✅ Based in the U.S. — ready for this once-in-a-lifetime experience

Think you’ve got what it takes — or know someone who does?
📩 Apply now!

items.text:
Palmera Entertainment Job Offer 🩷

 JOB: DANCERS 🕺

🇬🇧UK CITIZENS ARE WELCOME! 🇬🇧

🌞 – Male & female, Dancers Under the Greek Sun! 🇬🇷🕺🎤

(EU citizens & non-EU residents with a valid EU residence permit welcome)

This is your last chance to land a paid summer job in paradise for last Months !
Palmera Entertainment is hiring for the final dancer and singer positions at 5★ resorts in the beautiful Greek Islands.
If you love the stage, sun, and sea – this job is for you.
🎭 Available Roles:
 • Dancer / performer 
 • Singer / Performer
📍 Location: 5★ Hotels – Greek Islands
📅 Contract Dates: 01 October – October 31st, 2025
📄 Swiss employment contract
💶 Net Salary: €900-1200€ /month + commissions ( depends on positions& experiences)
🎬 See what we do🎭
👉 Watch our showreel : https://youtu.be/9PdbLO--GX4?si=W8fKURLEWPjE9bCG 
✅ We Offer:
 • 🏡 Free accommodation
 • 🍽️ Full board (3 meals/day) + drinks included in the main restaurant 
 • 🚖 Free transfer from airport to hotel
 • 📶 Free internet & laundry service 
 • 🧥 Free uniforms
 • 🎓 Free rehearsals and show training
 • 🧳 €200-300€ travel bonus (paid at contract end)
 • 🛡️ Full insurance (accident, pension, social)
 • 💰 Extra bonuses for merchandising promo
 • ☀️ An unforgettable summer experience
🕒 Typical Workday (6~8 hrs)
 • 🎭 4-5 performances/week, 1 hour per show
 • 🎬 Rehearsals: As needed (usually midday)
Schedules can vary slightly by hotel and concept – flexibility is key.
🌍 You Need To Be:
 • An EU citizen 
 • Energetic, outgoing, team-oriented
 • Experienced or passionate about dance, singing, or performing
 Nn• Confident engaging with international hotel guests
 • Fully available from September  to October 2025

Instagram: palmera_entertainment
TikTok: palmera_entertainment

💬 Don’t miss your chance and shine with Palmera  !☀️🎶🌴 apply now @ : adriano@palmera-agency.com

items.text:
Hi everyone, I'm Deividas 30, Lithuanian.

Model | Performer | Wellness Professional
With over 50 professional photoshoots under my belt — including paid projects across fashion, lifestyle, artistic, body paint, and life modeling — I have developed a versatile presence in front of the camera backed by a disciplined lifestyle and unique skillset.

Link below intro video
https://drive.google.com/file/d/19OcejTSRFWF2ZmQxdeoF92CEF7TKKAdb/view?usp=drivesdk

Alongside modeling, I bring on-screen experience from multiple TV shows, interview formats, podcasts, and extra appearances in my home country, while continuously expanding into acting and performance-based work.

Performance Skills
• Aerial Acrobatics — Hoop, Trapeze, Silks, Rope (Beginner–Intermediate)
• Contact Fire Staff — Intermediate
• Katana Wielding — Intermediate 
• Yoga — Advanced
• Swimming — Advanced
• Parkour - Intermediate
• Dancing - non professional but confident dancer

I’m currently seeking freelance work as model/actor/performer and agency representation (available internationally). Open to test shoots, collaborations, and paid opportunities.

✨ Updated measurements (as of Sept 22, 2025):
Height: 195cm
Chest: 41
Waist: 32
Hips: 37.5
Neck: 16
Sleeve: 32 (81.5cm)
Inseam: 32 (81.5cm)
Outseam: 36.4 (92.3cm)
Shoulder Width: 19 (48.5cm)
Shoe: UK 10.5 (can do 10–11) | EU 44–46

🌍 Based in London | Available worldwide

Professional Background
• Qualified Swimming Coach, Yoga Teacher, and Personal Trainer with 12+ years of teaching experience.
• Deep expertise in health, movement, breath, wellness, and high performance.

What Sets Me Apart
• Strong work ethic, relentless discipline, and ability to perform under discomfort, pressure, and challenging conditions.
• Holistic approach to self-regulation — always camera-ready, physically prepared, mentally sharp, and adaptable.
• Highly motivated in building my craft and presence — I create, edit, and post content daily across YouTube, TikTok, and Instagram to develop audience reach and on-camera charisma.

Current Focus
Seeking opportunities in modeling, acting, and performance — primarily in the UK (based in London ) but open to international projects. I’m committed to levelling up my skills, embracing bold creative challenges, and bringing exceptional authentic energy, professionalism, and reliability to every collaboration.

If you need anything else please let me know 

Kindest regards 
Deividas Juozapavičius
+12022558377
Instagram: @deivjuo
YouTube: @deivjuo
TikTok: @deivjuo

items.text:
Hi Everyone!

I'm a student studying filmmaking at **Birmingham City University**, and for one of our assignments, we are creating a **short film** and are looking for actors.

The concept isn't decided yet, but we are deciding between two:
1. A past chess champion reminisces about his glory days and replays the match that he lost in which started his downfall.
2. A girl whose inner self is screaming at her to help, while she is sucked into her phone, a film themed on how addicted we are to our phones.

We have a Test Shoot Day on the 23rd of October, 9:00am-12:00pm, and the Shoot Day is on the 4th of November, 9:00am-4:00pm. Both are at Parkside Building, Birmingham City University.

As we are students, this will be unpaid, unfortunately. But this is a great opportunity for actors who are starting out and want to get something on their resumes. We will include you in the credits.

We will have more details before the shoot, so don't worry.

If you are interested, please send an email to this address: **maisie.condron@mail.bcu.ac.uk**

Please include this information:

- Name

- Age

- Sex

- Location

- A self-tape of any performance

We will also be having more films come up in the future, so if you don't fit any of the roles described, you can still send an application in!

Thank you!

sharedPost.text:
The Foundry Acting Studio

Where Professional Training Meets Real Opportunity

At The Foundry Acting Studio, we believe every actor deserves a world class education without barriers, hidden costs, or false promises.

Our curriculum…. built and refined over six years,  is internationally recognised, exceeding Spotlight’s accreditation requirements by more than three times. We are Spotlight approved, SAG recognised, and currently in talks with other major organisations worldwide. Our work is supported by acclaimed writers, directors, and actors connected to some of the most influential platforms in the industry.

What makes us different:
 • World Class Curriculum: Designed to equal the top schools in the world, yet offered at a fraction of the cost.
 • No Hidden Tiers or Costs: Every actor receives the same training. There are no “higher levels,” upsells, or paywalls. Your talent is never defined by your wallet.
 • Personal Coaching: We keep classes small, so every actor is seen, heard, and individually assessed with hands on guidance.
 • No Agency Agenda: We are not an agency. You will never pay us for a promise of representation. Our focus is training and opportunity, not commission.
 • Industry Films: We are the only UK studio guaranteeing work by producing industry standard films with RED and ARRI cameras…. work that goes directly on your Spotlight profile.
 • Equality & Integrity

At The Foundry Acting Studio, we believe in building the industry, not dividing it. For that reason, we do not accept students who are currently in the middle of a paid term with another school or who are tied to an agency that is directly run by that same school. We respect the work of fellow coaches and do not believe in poaching actors away from their commitments.

Once an actor has completed their term elsewhere and is no longer represented under an agency attached to another school, they are welcome to join us for a fresh start. This ensures absolute fairness, integrity, and clarity for everyone involved.

Because The Foundry is not an agency, your place with us is never tied to representation. When you train here, your development is entirely about your craft. If you do not currently have an agent, our team will guide you toward finding one that best suits your path, independent, professional representation that has nothing to do with paying for classes.

We believe this creates a healthier, more transparent industry for all… actors, coaches, and agencies alike.

 • Accessibility: Whether you are working full-time, on benefits, retired, or just beginning your journey, our training is affordable and inclusive. Discounts are available for civil servants.
 • Expanding Opportunities: Teen classes are launching soon, and new locations are opening across the UK.

Our Philosophy

When you walk through our doors, you are not a number, not a “pound sign,” and never a currency. You are an actor, with equal right to professional training, opportunity, and growth.

At The Foundry, we believe in community. We believe in supporting fellow actors, fellow coaches, headshot photographers, showreel specialists, fight choreographers, and everyone who contributes to the craft. Together, we build the industry.

Ready to Join?

Direct message us today for full details on class times, dates, and locations near you. Step into a studio that is reshaping the future of acting in the UK and beyond.

The Foundry Acting Studio
Professional. Inclusive. Respected. Recognised

items.text:
Rainhill Garrick Society are performing ‘ Habeus Corpus’ by Alan Bennett on February 12th-14th 2026.

Alan Bennett’s Habeus Corpus is set some time in the Seventies and follows the lives of the Wicksteed family. The story follows Dr and Muriel Wicksteed as they both seek pleasure and fun outside of their marital relationship. The farcical play is very fast paced, incredibly funny and occasionally surreal. The bumbling sex-obsessed British characters such as the virginal vicar, the ﬂat chested spinster, the peering doctor, his frustrated wife and of course a bra salesman man all come together in this bizarre and thoroughly entertaining story.

Parts available:-

Dennis Wicksteed - the hypochondriac son of Dr Wickseed, (20-30)

Felicity Rumpers - young, nubile, upper class  (20-30)

Constance Wicksteed - the sister of Dr Wicksteed, flat chested and sex starved, (20+) 

Play read through Tuesday 21st October at 7.30 in Rainhill Village Hall
Auditions- Thursday 23rd October at 7.30 Rainhill Village Hall 
Rehearsals are on Tuesdays and Thursday evenings 7.30-9.30 and the 3 Sundays prior to the performance.
Audition pieces are available on request. 

We are an amateur group so the roles are unpaid, but we are a well respected group of 83 years standing who enjoy great support from a large dedicated audience. 
The play is great fun with some slapstick and music but with some poignant moments that say a lot about relationships.

For further information contact: sophiebrogan99@gmail.com

Do realizacji krótkich filmów społecznych poszukujemy aktora do głównej roli: 

Mężczyzna, 50–55 lat 

siwiejące włosy, możliwy lekki brzuszek, zwyczajny wygląd „pracownika biurowego” – naturalny, niewyidealizowany. 

Nagrania: 24.09.2025 

Miejsce: Fuzja, Łódź 

Stawka: 500 zł netto 

Na planie: krótka wypowiedź do kamery, nagrania prostych przebitek. 

Zgłoszenia: Prosimy o przesłanie krótkiego wideo oraz 2–3 aktualnych zdjęć na adres: praca@goodeye.com.pl 

Zastrzegamy, że skontaktujemy się wyłącznie z wybranymi kandydatami. 

Szczegóły projektu przekażemy osobom zaproszonym do współpracy.

**WARSZAWA / ŻYRARDÓW / SOCHACZEW**

**30 września i 11 października**

Szukam Statystów na plan filmu krótkometrażowego na 2 dni kontynuacyjne.

- Plan 30 września jest w Puszczy Mariańskiej niedaleko Żyrardowa.
-Plan 11 października w Sochaczewie.

Gramy lata 70te, nie ma wymagań co do wyglądu i wieku.

Dojazd we własnym zakresie dlatego szukam osób z autem, które zgodzą się zabrać 2/3 lub nawet 4 osoby.

Jest zwrot kosztów paliwa.

Plan kameralny, zapewnione pełne wyżywienie, jest gdzie spocząć 

**Stawka 130 zł za dzień zdjęciowy. Łącznie 260 zł za 2 dni**

W zgłoszeniu poproszę informację odnośnie auta. Pasażer czy Kierowca? 

ZGŁOSZENIA:

Poproszę na adres: **ewelina.wika@podtytulem.pl**

W tytule maila: **FILM K2**

W treści: imię i nazwisko, wiek, nr telefonu, miejscowość

W załączniku:

– aktualne, dobrej jakości zdjęcie twarzy (portret, w dziennym świetle, bez filtrów)

There has never been a better time for older performers to return to the industry. Right now, there’s a huge demand for actors over 50.If you’ve taken a break  whether to raise a family, pursue another career, or simply step away for a while  this is the moment to come back. As you get older, there’s less competition, and the life experience you’ve gained only strengthens your craft.

Sometimes that time away gives you exactly what you need to succeed when you return: perspective, resilience, and real-world skills that shine on screen and stage.

Remember  there’s a role for every age, and the industry is waiting for you.
#marksummers #marksummerscasting #castingdirector #olderwiserstronger #actors #castingcall

topComments.text: I've stepped my toe in at 46 and had a ball. Looking for more experience if you know of any particular castings for over 40s. Kindest regards x

sharedPost.text:
Movietime September 2025, The Third

EINE WARMHERZIGE STORY ŰBER BRÜDER UND EIN NEUES MAGISCHES SCHULJAHR STARTET

Die zweite Septemberhälfte bringt nicht nur Leonardo Di Caprio zurück ins Kino (Stadtkino Center Laa), sondern es beginnt ein neues Jahr mit der SCHULE DER MAGISCHEN TIERE 4 (Babylon Kino, Filmbühne Waidhofen/Ybbs).

Einem ungleichen Brüderpaar begegnet man in GANZER HALBER BRUDER (Stadtkino Horn), wobei wir mit dem Hauptdarsteller Christoph Maria Herbst ein paar Worte plaudern durften.

Der Ö Film hat weitere Highlights parat, wo wir in der Sendung auch 2 Interviews mit den RegisseurInnen führen konnten. NARBEN EINES PUTSCHES oder HOW TO BE NORMAL AND THE ODDNESS OF THE OTHER WORLD (Kronenkino Mistelbach).

In den Lichtspielen Gföhl gibt es Ende September einen besonderen Event mit dem Filmarchiv Austria und wir trafen eine Zeitzeugin, die im Sitzendorfer Kino noch die Sissi-Filme gesehen hat.

Abgerundet wird das Kinomagazin musikalisch in Memoriam Robert Redford, in dem wir Songs und Themes seiner besten Filme präsentieren.

Mittwoch 24.09.2025 von 17 bis 19h EXKLUSIV auf radioYpsilon 94.5 oder via Stream (http://mp3.radioypsilon.at:8000/)

items.text:
Dear Actors, 

Join me Saturday for a free 75-minute ONLINE class: HOW TO CHOOSE A MONOLOGUE FOR ANY AUDITION.  Participants can read or perform monologues for feedback  and I cover a LOT about choosing monologues, including . . .

• How to find material that’s great for you
• Where to look
• How to recognize good material
• Choosing well for specific kinds of auditions
• Building a killer repertoire
• Effective cutting and editing
• When and when not to do overdone monologues
• The “Hello, This Is Me” monologue and why it’s so incredibly valuable for auditioning actors

To reserve, email classes@monologueaudition.com

**Can't do this one? Email classes@monologueaudition.com to join my list and hear about next classes and free events :) **

You can also visit my website, MonologueAudition.com for Monologue FAQ, Monday Morning Monologues (free feedback on Mondays), a short film about how I teach monologues, and much more :) 

~Karen 

KAREN KOHLHAAS is a director and founding ensemble member of the Atlantic Theater Company and senior teacher at the Atlantic Acting School. She teaches her own online classes in monologues, cold reading, scene study, and directing, and is the author of The Monologue Audition: A Practical Guide for Actors (recommended by Helen Mirren in her Master Class on acting, and a Backstage must-read); and How to Choose a Monologue for Any Audition. She was named Best NYC Monologue Teacher and Best NYC Cold Reading Teacher by Backstage readers.

She was named Best NYC Monologue Teacher and Best NYC Cold Reading Teacher by Backstage readers.

items.text:
CASTING CALL

We’re looking for a female actor to join us this December for our RAPUNZEL pantomime (school tour). 

We’re casting either of the following parts, with our existing performer playing the opposite role. 

- Rapunzel (lead)
- Gothel (villain)

Last year was our best selling tour - but we hope to beat that this year! Because it’s schools, the shows are weekday mornings and early afternoons, so you’ll have your evenings and weekends free. The performances are in the Norfolk, Suffolk and Cambridge area. 

We’re currently offering a minimum of £870 - which will go up as we get more bookings in + travel expenses. 
The tour spans from 1st - 19th December 2025. 
Aiming to start weekly rehearsals asap - in Hunstanton (PE36). These are unpaid but we keep them as flexible as possible.

This will be our thirteenth panto tour, and we’ve built up a good name in the area, with schools booking us year after year (even before we announce the title!) We pride ourselves on being a warm, friendly, but professional company.

If interested, please get in touch for further details - either by a PM on here, or via email - purple-dreams@hotmail.co.uk - I’m looking forward to hearing from (some of) you 🙂

Many thanks
Tobias Nicholls
Creative Director 
Purple Dreams Productions

INTENSE CRIME DRAMA - SHORT (PAID)

1-day shoot in London (UK) for 2nd week in October 2025 (date tbc)

(For actors based in the London area).

 

Summary: A night of heavy drinking ends in a deadly contest between newfound besties - a fearless Nigerian gangland enforcer and a trigger-happy European gunman.

 

This project is Episode #0 of ‘Brave Hunter in Ghost City’  - introducing a new African story world and some of its main characters. ** **

 

MALE LEAD: to play fearless gangland enforcer.  Black African, 25-45, Lagos accent, 5’6”+, athletic physique with good fitness and conditioning. Stage combat training. Flat rate of £300 for 15 hours.

 

MALE LEAD: to play trigger-happy gunman. White European,  35-45, 5’ 6”+, 85kg-100kg,  powerful physique with good fitness and conditioning. Stage combat training. Flat rate of £300 for 15 hours.

 

SUPPORTING MALE: to play dead gangster. White European, 35-45, 5’ 6”+, 80kg-100kg. Half a day of shooting for £150 for 7 hours.

 

You will need professional experience playing character roles on Stage, Film or TV. Please send in a cover letter, your CV with headshot and your showreel to Davina Brown at k2Filmworks@gmail.com

+++ Kompars:innen gesucht für Debüt-Kinofilm „DIE MATRIARCHIN“ (AT) von Alison Kuhn +++

📆 14.10.2025 in Berlin

🏙 Motiv: Fußgängerzone – Schüler:innen auf dem Weg nach Hause

💶 Tagesgage: 80€ bis maximal 6h (+45min Pause)

Wir suchen noch junge Komparserie wohnhaft in Berlin im Alter von 18-21 Jahren! Zeitlich voraussichtlich 8 bis 13:00 Uhr!

Inhalt: Die 17-jährige Kim muss sich ihre Plattenbauwohnung an der deutschen Ostsee nicht nur mit ihrer vietnamesischen Mutter und ihrem kleinen Bruder Bao teilen, sondern auch mit jeder Menge wildfremden Vietnames:innen. Die Mutter betreibt in ihrem kleinen Brautmodeladen eine Agentur für illegale Schleusungen aus Vietnam nach Europa. Kim möchte mit allen Mitteln ihrer Mutter gefallen und eines Tages die Agentur übernehmen. Als sich endlich eine Chance ergibt, wird sie sich schnell bewusst, was das wirklich für sie bedeutet.

Es ist keine Vorerfahrung nötig! 🎬

Meldet euch mit KOMPARSERIE BERLIN im Betreff, Fotos von euch an:

📩 diematriarchin.extras@gmail.com

**Hey ihr Lieben 👋,**

wir sind eine junge **Supplement-Marke aus Deutschland** und suchen **UGC Creatorinnen** für spannende Projekte 🇩🇪🎥

👉 Gesucht sind:
* deutschsprachige, junge Creatorinnen (idealerweise U30)
* sportlich, kreativ und selbstbewusst vor der Kamera
* Erfahrung mit **authentischen Handyaufnahmen** (Talking Head Clips, kurze Story-Videos etc.)

Wir schicken dir unser Produkt zu und du erstellst:
* **Talking Head Videos**
* **individuelle Clips** für Social Media

💸 Das Projekt ist **bezahlt** und bei guter Zusammenarbeit sind **regelmäßige Folgeaufträge** sehr wahrscheinlich!

Wenn du Interesse hast:
➡️ Kommentiere unter diesem Beitrag oder schreib mir eine DM ✨

Freue mich auf eure Nachrichten!
— Malou von PureMoss

items.text:
Hallo, mein Name ist Mojtaba.
Ich habe eine große Leidenschaft für Werbung, Modeln und Schauspiel im Kino.
Vor der Kamera zu stehen ist meine Arbeit und meine Leidenschaft – darin habe ich bereits wertvolle Erfahrungen gesammelt.

Ich spreche mehrere Sprachen und kann in internationalen Projekten mitwirken.
Gerne übernehme ich auch Auftritte für Werbung auf Plattformen wie TikTok, Instagram oder Facebook.

Wenn Sie Interesse haben, lade ich Sie herzlich ein, mit mir zusammenzuarbeiten. Vielen Dank!

Are you looking for a Performing Arts College in the Buckinghamshire area?

We are excited to share our next Experience day and Audition date for our 2026 intake 💫

If you are in year 10 or 11 and would like to see what a day at The Performers Hub is like come and join us on the 15th of November! 

For more information or to book your place email info@theperformershub.co.uk 

You can also register for your place on the website. Click on "Register now"  
https://www.theperformershub.co.uk/

items.text:
Hi everyone, I'm Deividas 30, Lithuanian.

Model | Performer | Wellness Professional
With over 50 professional photoshoots under my belt — including paid projects across fashion, lifestyle, artistic, body paint, and life modeling — I have developed a versatile presence in front of the camera backed by a disciplined lifestyle and unique skillset.

Link below intro video
https://drive.google.com/file/d/19OcejTSRFWF2ZmQxdeoF92CEF7TKKAdb/view?usp=drivesdk

Alongside modeling, I bring on-screen experience from multiple TV shows, interview formats, podcasts, and extra appearances in my home country, while continuously expanding into acting and performance-based work.

Performance Skills
• Aerial Acrobatics — Hoop, Trapeze, Silks, Rope (Beginner–Intermediate)
• Contact Fire Staff — Intermediate
• Katana Wielding — Intermediate 
• Yoga — Advanced
• Swimming — Advanced
• Parkour - Intermediate
• Dancing - non professional but confident dancer

I’m currently seeking freelance work as model/actor/performer and agency representation (available internationally). Open to test shoots, collaborations, and paid opportunities.

✨ Updated measurements (as of Sept 22, 2025):
Height: 195cm
Chest: 41
Waist: 32
Hips: 37.5
Neck: 16
Sleeve: 32 (81.5cm)
Inseam: 32 (81.5cm)
Outseam: 36.4 (92.3cm)
Shoulder Width: 19 (48.5cm)
Shoe: UK 10.5 (can do 10–11) | EU 44–46

🌍 Based in London | Available worldwide

Professional Background
• Qualified Swimming Coach, Yoga Teacher, and Personal Trainer with 12+ years of teaching experience.
• Deep expertise in health, movement, breath, wellness, and high performance.

What Sets Me Apart
• Strong work ethic, relentless discipline, and ability to perform under discomfort, pressure, and challenging conditions.
• Holistic approach to self-regulation — always camera-ready, physically prepared, mentally sharp, and adaptable.
• Highly motivated in building my craft and presence — I create, edit, and post content daily across YouTube, TikTok, and Instagram to develop audience reach and on-camera charisma.

Current Focus
Seeking opportunities in modeling, acting, and performance — primarily in the UK (based in London ) but open to international projects. I’m committed to levelling up my skills, embracing bold creative challenges, and bringing exceptional authentic energy, professionalism, and reliability to every collaboration.

If you need anything else please let me know 

Kindest regards 
Deividas Juozapavičius
+12022558377
Instagram: @deivjuo
YouTube: @deivjuo
TikTok: @deivjuo

🎭 **Actors! Feeling stuck or discouraged?**
 Unlock more **joy, ease, and creativity** in your acting journey with just a few simple mindset shifts.

✨ In this quick video, you'll learn **3 powerful phrases** that can transform the way you speak to yourself — and how that impacts your career.

Words have energy. Use them to empower, not limit yourself.

👉 Watch now: [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zjhM5VXYktM](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zjhM5VXYktM) 
Shifting your mindset through how you speak to yourself can unlock more joy, ease, creativity, and trust in your acting journey.

🎬CASTING FELHÍVÁS – belső felhasználású pénzügyi videó🎬 

Forgatás: 2025. szeptember 25. (csütörtök)
Helyszín: Budapest
Díjazás: megegyezés szerint

Keresett szerepek:
 •  Férfi, 40–45 éves – jó megjelenésű, „jómódú családapa” karakter
 •  Nő, 35–40 éves, aki a feleséget játsza
 •  Két gyermek, 10–12 éves (szülők jelentkezését várjuk)
 •  pár szerepét játszó fiú és lány jelentkezését várjuk 28–32 éves
        •        Férfi, aki kaszás jelmezben eljátssza a halált (életkori megkötés nincs)

Jelentkezéshez küldd el:
 • 1–2 friss fotót
 • Rövid bemutatkozó videót (max. 1 perc; név, életkor, tapasztalat)

E-mail: szerepelj.casting@gmail.com
Kérjük a tárgyba írd be: „Pénzügyi videó – [szerep] – [név]” (pl. „Pénzügyi videó – Gyermek – Kiss Anna”).

items.text:
This is for those who seek an intimate unique experience…

The Shop For Mortals and Fools
Opening soon in Central
london. Only for select customers.

Old relics, curious finds, hidden trinkets, and heirlooms – treasures that whisper forgotten stories. In this enigmatic shop, a select audience is invited to an exclusive preview of its mysterious collection.

Inspired by Euripides’ The Bacchae, this bold production delves into one of the greatest tragedies ever written, weaving an original and compelling narrative that explores power, vengeance. The production transforms a disused space into an atmospheric shop, a mythic world where gods, mortals, and unsuspecting customers collide in the voice of a woman.

Mystery awaits. Don’t miss out – join the curious and fools, book your tickets today! https://www.tickettailor.com/events/theshopformortalsandallfools

And get this exclusive discount: F00ls100 or F00ls200

Co-Produced by Stanley Arts  photo with Kate Webster and photo by James Lawson Stanley ArtsKate WebsterJames Lawson@

items.summary:
This is for those who seek an intimate unique experience…

The Shop For Mortals and Fools
Opening soon in Central
london. Only for select customers.

Old relics, curious finds, hidden trinkets, and heirlooms – treasures that whisper forgotten stories. In this enigmatic shop, a select audience is invited to an exclusive preview of its mysterious collection.

Inspired by Euripides’ The Bacchae, this bold production delves into one of the greatest tragedies ever written, weaving an original and compelling narrative that explores power, vengeance. The production transforms a disused space into an atmospheric shop, a mythic world where gods, mortals, and unsuspecting customers collide in the voice of a woman.

Mystery awaits. Don’t miss out – join the curious and fools, book your tickets today! https://www.tickettailor.com/events/theshopformortalsandallfools

And get this exclusive discount: F00ls100 or F00ls200

Co-Produced by Stanley Arts  photo with Kate Webster and photo by James Lawson Stanley ArtsKate WebsterJames Lawson@

Vi søger et par(helst et ægte par) 28 - 35 år til en reklame film for et forsikringsselskab.
Er man gravid er det et plus - men ikke et krav 

**D. 8. Oktober kl 9 - 17**

**København**

Har det interesse, så skriv til os på cast@plotworks.dk

Husk at sende **billeder / video** med.

God ide også at inkludere mobilnummer, så vi nemt kan få fat på jer.

Kommentar og privatbeskeder besvares ikke

sharedPost.text:
EKSTRA-AUDITION PÅ NY MUSICAL 🎭🎶 
Mandlige sangere/skuespillere (eller dansere) i alderen 18-35 år søges især, men alle køn og aldre fra 18 år og op er velkomne til ekstra-audition (uanset erfaring) på Musicalteatrets store 20 års jubilæumsforestilling (for voksne), “JEG TROR DER KALDES KÆRLIGHED: THE MUSICAL”, der skal opføres i april/maj 2026 på Folketeatrets Store Turnéscene i København! Tilmeld dig audition nu: musicalteatret.dk/audition

Den nostalgiske, nye musicalkomedie er spækket med 25 af de største klassikere fra Børnenes Grand Prix i 00’erne, bl.a. “Kickflipper”, “Arabiens drøm”, “Tro på os to”, “Turbofluen”, “Du er ikke som de andre pi’r”, “Stop stop”, “Du ka’ sige ja-ja,” “Shake Shake Shake” og mange flere. Køb billetter til forestillingen allerede nu på Billetlugen: bit.ly/musical2026

Ekstra-audition finder sted lørdag d. 4. oktober 2025 i Musicalteatrets faste øvelokaler på Frederiksberg nær hovedstadens centrum. Det er muligt “kun” at gå til audition som danser, hvis man ikke ønsker at have replikker/synge.

“JEG TROR DET KALDES KÆRLIGHED: THE MUSICAL”
April/maj 2026 • Folketeatrets Store Turnéscene.
Instruktør/forfatter: Rasmus Mansachs.
Sanginstruktør/korleder: Johnny Jørgensen.
Koreografer: Frederikke Dencker Rasmussen & Anne-Cathrine Albæk.

EKSTRA-AUDITION:
Lørdag d. 4. oktober 2025.
Der søges i alt 30-35 skuespillere, solister, korsangere, ensemblemedlemmer og/eller dansere til forestillingen. OBS: Vær opmærksom på de opdaterede rammer for prøver i påskehelligdagene op til premieren i 2026.
Læs alt om ekstra-audition (og tilmeld dig) her: musicalteatret.dk/audition

BILLETSALG:
Læs mere om forestillingen og køb billetter allerede nu på Billetlugen (egnet fra 10 år og op): bit.ly/musical2026

🎬 Schauspielerin gesucht! 🎬 {No Budget}

Für einen US-Horror-Kurzfilmwettbewerb suche ich noch eine Darstellerin.

📽️ Eckdaten:

Kurzfilm max. 5 Minuten Länge

Fertigstellung bis 13. Oktober

1 Tag Brainstorming/Planung 
1 Drehtag

Ort: Ingolstadt+Umgebung (Bayern)

Spielalter: 18–35 Jahre

Freude am Horror-Genre 

📌 Wichtig
Wir treffen uns zunächst einen Tag zum gemeinsamen Brainstorming.

Bitte melde dich nur, wenn du problemlos nach Ingolstadt kommen kannst.

📬 Interesse?

Dann schicke mir gerne dein Portfolio oder ein paar Infos über dich!

**$500 Finders Fee: Have You Been Ghosted By Your Husband Or Wife? (Docu-Series Casting)**

An acclaimed television production company and a major cable network are actively searching for women and men whose spouse has suddenly and mysteriously vanished, without warning, without explanation, and with no way to contact them. If you are still *legally married* but don’t know *where *your spouse is, you don’t have a clear explanation or *“why”* they left, or *how* to reach them, *we want to hear your story for a bold and empowering new series.*

**$500 Referral Fee: **Do You Know Someone? Share their information with us or simply have them tell us you referred them! Finders fee is paid IF referral is selected for production. 

*Selected for series candidates are compensated for taking part as well as receive expert help in tracking down their missing spouse, rebuilding their lives and finding closure. *

**To apply, please email: ****[casting@bodegapictures.com](mailto:casting@bodegapictures.com)****, **or visit: https://abandonedspouseshortapp.castingcrane.com/

items.text:
Hello all, this is another post for a different student film happening on Auraria Campus. I am not involved in this one, I am posting to this group for the producer since he is not on Facebook. So if you are interested in this one please contact the producer. 

Producer- Brennan Jones bjones89@msudenver.edu 

Production Title- The Cost of Greed 

Production Dates- Exact dates are not set but filming will be in October 

Logline- Peter and Henry are sent on a treasure hunt to a house that is believed to be abandoned. Where they then discover it's not a treasure hunt after all and they must face their greed. Either take the treasure or leave empty handed. 

Peter (19-25) Male 

Peter has a moral compass that he deals with during this film. He wants to do the right thing and in the end that pays off for him. 

Henry (19-25) Male 

Henry is a billionaire with no need for more money, however that does not stop him from thinking he needs more. He is corrupt and in the end karma gets to him. 

Audition Dates- September 18th-September 29th

Audition Location- Email-Self Tape

This is a student film for a final project therefore this film is non paid and non union.

Contact Email- bjones89@msudenver.edu 

Must contact the producer to be consider for the role. Once you contact Brennan he will send you the audition material.

Casting Call – Mandlig skuespiller/statist søges

Vi er et hold på seks studerende fra VIA Film & Transmedia i Aarhus. I forbindelse med et skoleprojekt samarbejder vi med designer Fie Nielsen og hendes studie, Fjör Studio, om branding af en ny tøjkollektion.

Kollektionen udforsker, hvad det vil sige at være mand i dag, og leger med udtryk, der udfordrer de traditionelle forestillinger om styrke, følelser og identitet.

Vi søger en mand i alderen 17–30 år, ca. 180 cm høj, almindelig af bygning og med tøjstørrelse small–medium.

Praktisk info
 Optagelserne finder sted i Skanderborg
 Mandag den 22/9
 Kl. 09.00–17.00

Projektet er frivilligt, men vi sørger selvfølgelig for mad, drikke, transport – og en sjov oplevelse samt muligheden for at få et spændende projekt på CV’et.

Kontakt Fredrik på (+45) 2285 1519 eller 354549@via.dk, hvis du er interesseret. 

Vi glæder os til at høre fra dig!

The first 10 mins of my first full length play Blackout 1985 is going to be performed as part of Wooden Arrow Productions next scratch evening on 30th October at Lamda at their Sainsburys Theatre!

The casting is UNPAID but there will be professional photography, industry guests for feedback and a chance to network after with the guests and the audience. There are also other roles in other plays that need filling. 

Deadline is this Saturday!

Synopsis of Blackout 1985: 28th September 1985. A day marked in history. The Lewis family gathers in their living room as the streets outside erupt in flames. Winston and Angie strive to protect their children, Jimmy and Asha, from a world that denies their humanity. As generational wounds, dreams, and tensions collide, the family must decide whether to stay safe behind closed doors or step into the fire of history. Blackout 1985 is the first in the trilogy, which shines a light on key Black British moments.

If you are interested or know anyone please go to this link - https://forms.gle/uJFMiQzyR6kVqBae8

items.text:
# **Casting Call: Student Short Film **

We are currently casting for two lead roles in our upcoming short film, filming at the beginning of November.

**Logline:**

A family gathers for dinner at a tarot-themed restaurant, but as the cards are drawn, buried secrets surface—turning a simple night out into an inescapable reckoning.

# **Roles:**

**ROBERT** (Male, 45–55)

The head of the family and a successful businesman. Robert appears to have it all — the career, the looks, the picture-perfect family. But beneath his composed, masculine exterior lies a man quietly suffocating, worn down by a life built on duty and expectations rather than desire. Over the course of the dinner, the cracks in his façade widen, pushing him toward a mental and emotional breaking point. This role requires strong range, balancing authority, charisma, and the slow unraveling into vulnerability and collapse.

**MADISON** (Female, 18–25)

The golden girl and youngest in the family, Madison is gorgeous, accomplished, and everyone’s clear favorite. On the surface, she embodies perfection — beauty, brains, and charm — but beneath that polish lies a calculating edge. She knows how to use her “pretty privilege” to her advantage, and she’s smart enough to make it her power. Yet the flawless image she projects is fragile, threatened by a secret that could shatter it in an instant. The role calls for a nuanced performance that blends charm, wit, and the darker undertones of ambition and self-preservation.

# **Shoot Details:**
* **Filming Dates:** 3rd to 6th November (4 consecutive days)
* **Time:** 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM daily
* **Location:** W5 3HN (West London)
* **Rehearsal & Table Read **prior to filming days
* **Payment:** £400 total per role

# **How to Apply:**

If you’re interested, please **fill out the form below** and we’ll send you script excerpts for a self-tape.

[https://forms.gle/N4NPWpKDLSWnZAD46](https://forms.gle/N4NPWpKDLSWnZAD46) 

We are really excited to make this project happen and would love to have you on board! 

Thanks,
Liza

items.text:
📣 SHEFFIELD PROFIT-SHARE ACTING OPPORTUNITY 📣

Synopsis - Dennis Le'Claire, 'World's Greatest Actor', is missing - and it's opening night! It's a theatre production's worst nightmare, that is until Sebastian Paris, 'World's Greatest Understudy', arrives on the scene. But all is not as it seems, as talks of foul play begin to spread.

In this force of farce, take a peek behind the curtain at scheming stage hands, devious directors, and preposterous playwrights.

__________________

A big thanks to those who came to our first set of auditions on Monday - it was fantastic to see the characters come to life and you all brought your A-game. We're looking forward to the rest of the week!

Audition information
🗓️ Sat 27 (14.30-16.30) September
📍 Sharrow Community Forum
📽️ Self tapes accepted (forgelighttheatre@gmail.com)
🔗 in Instagram bio (forgelighttheatre) for more information and sign ups

sharedPost.text:
The Foundry Acting Studio

Where Professional Training Meets Real Opportunity

At The Foundry Acting Studio, we believe every actor deserves a world class education without barriers, hidden costs, or false promises.

Our curriculum…. built and refined over six years,  is internationally recognised, exceeding Spotlight’s accreditation requirements by more than three times. We are Spotlight approved, SAG recognised, and currently in talks with other major organisations worldwide. Our work is supported by acclaimed writers, directors, and actors connected to some of the most influential platforms in the industry.

What makes us different:
 • World Class Curriculum: Designed to equal the top schools in the world, yet offered at a fraction of the cost.
 • No Hidden Tiers or Costs: Every actor receives the same training. There are no “higher levels,” upsells, or paywalls. Your talent is never defined by your wallet.
 • Personal Coaching: We keep classes small, so every actor is seen, heard, and individually assessed with hands on guidance.
 • No Agency Agenda: We are not an agency. You will never pay us for a promise of representation. Our focus is training and opportunity, not commission.
 • Industry Films: We are the only UK studio guaranteeing work by producing industry standard films with RED and ARRI cameras…. work that goes directly on your Spotlight profile.
 • Equality & Integrity

At The Foundry Acting Studio, we believe in building the industry, not dividing it. For that reason, we do not accept students who are currently in the middle of a paid term with another school or who are tied to an agency that is directly run by that same school. We respect the work of fellow coaches and do not believe in poaching actors away from their commitments.

Once an actor has completed their term elsewhere and is no longer represented under an agency attached to another school, they are welcome to join us for a fresh start. This ensures absolute fairness, integrity, and clarity for everyone involved.

Because The Foundry is not an agency, your place with us is never tied to representation. When you train here, your development is entirely about your craft. If you do not currently have an agent, our team will guide you toward finding one that best suits your path, independent, professional representation that has nothing to do with paying for classes.

We believe this creates a healthier, more transparent industry for all… actors, coaches, and agencies alike.

 • Accessibility: Whether you are working full-time, on benefits, retired, or just beginning your journey, our training is affordable and inclusive. Discounts are available for civil servants.
 • Expanding Opportunities: Teen classes are launching soon, and new locations are opening across the UK.

Our Philosophy

When you walk through our doors, you are not a number, not a “pound sign,” and never a currency. You are an actor, with equal right to professional training, opportunity, and growth.

At The Foundry, we believe in community. We believe in supporting fellow actors, fellow coaches, headshot photographers, showreel specialists, fight choreographers, and everyone who contributes to the craft. Together, we build the industry.

Ready to Join?

Direct message us today for full details on class times, dates, and locations near you. Step into a studio that is reshaping the future of acting in the UK and beyond.

The Foundry Acting Studio
Professional. Inclusive. Respected. Recognised
